>> SMITH: I mean, is the town a
carcass, too?

00:19:02.160 --> 00:19:07.400
>> Well there is about 1,000
jobs that were lost here.
Close to 1,000 jobs.
>> SMITH: It seemed to me that

00:19:07.400 --> 00:19:17.000
