achieve.

00:21:42.900 --> 00:21:51.760
>> It's the heart of Wal-Mart's
pricing strategy.
Wal-Mart puts tremendous amount
of planning, organization, and

00:21:51.760 --> 00:21:58.700
thinking into what their opening
price points are going to be
based on last year's sales,
based on customer requests.

00:21:59.600 --> 00:22:07.060
>> SMITH: Every line of goods
