U.S. retailing and offshore
sourcing.

00:24:25.730 --> 00:24:32.560
>> There was a lot of talk about
those companies being asleep at
the wheel, being fat, dumb, and
happy, you know.

00:24:32.560 --> 00:24:37.000
And we didn't want to be fat,
dumb, and happy.
We wanted to be aggressive.
>> SMITH: And they were

00:24:37.000 --> 00:24:48.600
aggressive.
