mushroomed to 1,500 in 1990.

00:24:48.600 --> 00:24:57.060
In 1991, it overtook its long
established rivals to become the
nation's biggest retailer.
Then, surprisingly, Wal-Mart

00:24:57.060 --> 00:25:06.100
began having trouble.
