year later, with the economy
slow and sales sluggish, Wal-

00:25:06.100 --> 00:25:11.100
Mart's stock price slumped
badly.
>> And Wal-Mart got very
nervous.

00:25:11.100 --> 00:25:17.800
It got lower and lower and
approaching that $20 mark.
And that $20 mark seemed to be
the, like, the threshold.

00:25:17.800 --> 00:25:24.600
"If it gets down below $20, it's
going to be a panic."
>> SMITH: Wal-Mart's new
management needed to crank up

00:25:24.600 --> 00:25:32.630
sales and profits, and they hit
