>> I saw this, as a store
manager, an influx, a giant

00:25:32.630 --> 00:25:39.300
influx of imported merchandise
coming in.
The stores were inundated with
inventory.

00:25:39.300 --> 00:25:44.330
Inundated.
I mean, we had so much of this
cheap crap floating around the
store, we didn't know what to do

00:25:44.330 --> 00:25:48.730
with it.
>> SMITH: Lehman was so
overwhelmed with merchandise
