declining.

00:26:01.100 --> 00:26:06.700
And you do understand, Jon, that
these imports have a high
margin, a high markup, and
they're going to help your

00:26:06.700 --> 00:26:11.900
profit-and-loss statement.
They're going to help the
company's profit-and-loss
statement."

00:26:11.900 --> 00:26:17.560
>> SMITH: The impact was
dramatic and immediate.
>> The margins on the
merchandise that were coming in

00:26:17.560 --> 00:26:23.200
from the Wal-Mart import items
were incredible.
>> SMITH: Like what?
>> 60%, 70%, 80%.

00:26:23.200 --> 00:26:29.300
You know, incredible.
>> SMITH: Compared with what
from American-made items?
>> Well, compare that to an

00:26:29.300 --> 00:26:37.830
electric razor that you might be
