00:26:44.100 --> 00:26:46.030
>> That's absolutely right.

00:26:47.130 --> 00:26:53.530
>> SMITH: By the late '90s, Wal-
Mart was dependent on low-cost
Asian imports, and it began
pushing its American suppliers

00:26:53.530 --> 00:27:04.860
to follow Wal-Mart to Asia.
>> Their message to us,
