side, that it's difficult to
make that... make ends meet, if

00:28:05.960 --> 00:28:13.400
you're a business, by staying
here.
>> SMITH: You, as a producer of
socks for 30, 40 years, are you

00:28:13.400 --> 00:28:18.960
now going to find that you need
to put a production facility in
China?
>> Absolutely.

00:28:18.960 --> 00:28:26.400
For us to remain a viable
company over the long run, we
know we have to compete.

00:28:26.730 --> 00:28:33.460
>> Wal-Mart basically tells its
suppliers, "We need to get those
