00:33:02.500 --> 00:33:11.800
80% of those suppliers are in
China.
>> SMITH: Several hundred
employees work at the

00:33:11.800 --> 00:33:19.760
procurement center, keeping the
import pipeline full.
>> Wal-Mart gives Chinese
suppliers the specifications for

00:33:19.760 --> 00:33:25.400
Wal-Mart products, and they
teach those suppliers how to
meet those specifications.
They have to do with price.

00:33:25.400 --> 00:33:30.630
They have to do with quality.
They have to do with delivery
schedule.
