>> Wal-Mart is... they are very
shrewd people.

00:33:43.830 --> 00:33:52.100
They know that they have the
volume orders behind them and
they can go into a factory and
almost demand... "These are my

00:33:52.100 --> 00:33:57.130
lists of demands, and this is
what I need."
>> SMITH: Kenneth Chan is a Hong
Kong entrepreneur who used to

00:33:57.130 --> 00:34:03.130
supply Wal-Mart.
