manufacturers into one of their

00:34:03.130 --> 00:34:07.460
little negotiating booths and
auction them off and say, "This
is what we want."
>> Yeah, the big reverse auction

00:34:07.460 --> 00:34:12.460
kind of thing where they bid the
price as low as possible.
>> SMITH: What do they do?
>> Basically, they bring people

00:34:12.460 --> 00:34:21.530
into their offices and just put
